snippet.title: Millie Megavolte 8 Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Millie 8 on Steam. Early Access soon! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2831730/Millie_Megavolte_8_Millie_and_the_Mole_King/

Eight playable characters, one stage, one boss. It's not much but it's a start! Millie 8 is going into Early Access because I want the game to be the best it can be and I need your help.
